title: About
text: We’re a UCLA student team investigating how women’s education shapes health outcomes across countries at different stages of development. Our project examines links between education levels, access to care, and fertility patterns to explore this relationship.

title: Beyond the Classroom: How Education Shapes Women’s Health and Futures
text:
Digital Humanities 101 Project - Digital Divas
Group Members: Cynthia Du, Claire Hayashida, Tom Liu, Allison Lynn, Montserrat Munoz-Garcia, Koji Schafer
